import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './Components/App'
import {BrowserRouter as Router} from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(
  <Router>
      <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
  </Router>
,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
